OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJames Lovelock: Influential
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgreen thinker dies aged 103
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, British scientist James Lovelock, who  
OL,6, devoted his life to the global green   
OL,7, movement, has died on his 103rd        
OL,8, birthday, his family has said.         
OL,10,FHis 1960s Gaia theory Earth, from rocks
OL,11,Fto air, was one huge interconnected and
OL,12,Fself-regulating system formed the basis
OL,13,Fof much of climate science.            
OL,15,FAnd he had warned climate change could 
OL,16,Fbe a tipping point for the planet.     
OL,18,FBut his support for nuclear energy and 
OL,19,Ffor fracking attracted criticism from  
OL,20,Fother environmentalists.               
